## 🗃️ Models — `src/models/`

All models use Mongoose Schema + TypeScript interfaces. Each model has both a `.ts` source and a compiled `.js` file.

### `User.ts` — Main player profile
| Field | Type | Default | Description |
|---|---|---|---|
| `id` | String | — | Discord User ID (unique, indexed) |
| `username` | String | `'Unknown Traveler'` | Discord display name |
| `balance` | Number | `1000` | Currency balance |
| `level` | Number | `1` | Player level |
| `worldLevel` | Number | `1` | Battle world level |
| `experience` | Number | `0` | XP toward next level |
| `dailyClaimed` | Boolean | `false` | Daily reward claimed today |
| `weeklyClaimed` | Boolean | `false` | Weekly reward claimed |
| `lastGachaReset` | Date | `null` | Last gacha pull reset timestamp |
| `dailyPulls` | Number | `0` | Pulls used today |
| `extraPulls` | Number | `0` | Bonus pull credits |
| `pity` | Number | `0` | Current 5★ pity counter |
| `pity4` | Number | `0` | Current 4★ pity counter |
| `gacha_inventory` | Array | `[]` | Items: `{ name, type, ascension, refinement, count }` |
| `team` | `String[]` | `[]` | Up to 4 character names (slim storage) |
| `animals` | `Map<string, Map<string, number>>` | `{}` | `{ rarity: { animalKey: count } }` |
| `boosters` | `Map<string, any>` | `{}` | Active booster entries with expiry |
| `inventory` | Mixed[] | `[]` | General item inventory |
| `equipped` | `Map<string, any>` | `{}` | Currently equipped gear |
| `lootbox` | Number | `0` | Lootbox count |
| `stats` | Object | all zeros | `totalGambled, totalWon, totalLost, commandsUsed, won_riel, lost_riel` |
| `customPrefix` | String | `null` | Per-user main prefix override |
| `customSubPrefix` | String | `null` | Per-user short prefix override |
| `joinedAt` | Date | `Date.now` | Account creation timestamp |

### Other Models

| Model | Description |
|---|---|
| `Character.ts` | Gacha pool item: `name, game, rarity, type (character/weapon), element, role, emoji, image_url` |
| `CharacterCard.ts` | Singleton config for the active character showcase card (id: `'default'`) |
| `AnimalRegistry.ts` | Animal definitions: `key, name, emoji, rarity, value` |
| `Listener.ts` | Admin listener map: `adminId → targetUserId` |
| `TalkTarget.ts` | Admin talk target: `adminId → { channelId, serverId, setAt }` |
| `Promo.ts` | Promotional data schema |

