## 🚀 Deployment & Tooling

### npm Scripts

| Script | Command | Description |
|---|---|---|
| `start` | `node --no-deprecation dist/core/index.js` | Production start from compiled JS |
| `dev` | `nodemon --exec ts-node src/core/index.ts` | Dev server with hot reload |
| `build` | `tsc` | Compile TypeScript to `dist/` |
| `lint` | `eslint .` | Lint all source files |
| `format` | `prettier --write .` | Auto-format all files |
| `test` | `jest` | Run the Jest test suite |

### Key Dependencies

| Package | Purpose |
|---|---|
| `discord.js ^14.25.1` | Core Discord bot framework |
| `mongoose ^9.2.3` | MongoDB ODM |
| `sharp ^0.34.5` | High-performance image processing |
| `jimp ^0.22.10` | Pure-JS image manipulation (fallback) |
| `axios ^1.11.0` | HTTP client for external API calls |
| `node-cron ^3.0.2` | Scheduled jobs (daily reset) |
| `express ^4.18.2` | HTTP health check server |
| `winston ^3.19.0` | Production logging |
| `winston-daily-rotate-file ^5.0.0` | Log file rotation |
| `zod ^4.3.6` | Runtime environment validation |
| `pokedex-promise-v2 ^4.2.0` | PokéAPI client with auto-caching |
| `minio ^8.0.7` | S3-compatible object storage client |
| `dotenv ^16.6.1` | `.env` file loading |

### Docker / Railway Deployment
- **`Dockerfile`**: Standard Node.js production image. Copies `dist/` and runs `node dist/core/index.js`.
- **`Procfile`**: Defines the web process for Railway/Heroku-style deployments.
- **`docker-compose.yml`**: Local development orchestration.
- **`.railwayignore`**: Excludes dev files from Railway deployment builds.

---

## 🔄 Data Flow Summary

```
Discord Message
      ↓
messageCreate.js (Event)
      ↓
commandHandler lookup → client.commands.get(commandName)
      ↓
Command File { name, execute, aliases }
      ↓
Service Layer (CombatService / GachaService / EconomyService / AnimalService / ImageGenerationService)
      ↓
DatabaseService (Mongoose → MongoDB Atlas)
      ↓
Discord Reply (embed / image attachment)
```
